;; ── ION DEX Common Library ──────────────────────────────────────────
;; ⚠️ ION-Chain-Specific: This library replaces TON stdlib functions
;; (build_ctx, catch_ctx, etc.) that may not be available on ION chain.
;; Must be verified with the ION chain FunC compiler before deployment.
;;
;; Uses global-variable context model instead of polymorphic ctx.at()
;; because FunC functions cannot return both int and slice from the
;; same function signature.

